channel.title: Need help submitting my server to the Status Checker
channel.description:
Every time I submit my server to the Mopar Status checker, it says my server is offline... I set up PF and all that crap with my router, but it still wont let me submit it.
The server is online, because I can log in to it. (Or at least, I think it's online)
Any help? Is the status checker messes up?
